@page "/admin/servers"
@using RevolutionaryWebApp.Shared.Models.Enums

<AccessLimited RequiredAccess="GroupType.Admin" RedirectOnInsufficientPermission="@true">
    <h3>Servers</h3>

    <h4>Controlled Servers</h4>

    These are automatically managed servers managed through AWS API. Note that these haven't been used in recent years,
    but the capability to manage them is still kept around.

    <div class="mb-3"></div>

    <ControlledServers />

    <div class="mb-3"></div>
    <h4>External Runners</h4>

    These are external runners that connect to us and are not managed by this application,
    instead they need to be manually created and configured here to be used.

    <div class="mb-3"></div>

    <JobRunners />

    <DevCenterTitle>Servers</DevCenterTitle>
</AccessLimited>

